            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "\"Cmdline expanded\" is when UI2 expands the `cmd` window to show a message exceeding 'cmdheight' until the next keypress. That happens for all message \"triggers\", not exclusively those after \"interactive |:| cmdline\" so that confused me (b8a976af). I don't know a better name for it.",
