        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I would argue that when you're in insert mode, you expect `<CR>` to insert a newline and nothing else. I think ignoring the special behavior of `<CR>` in insert/terminal mode is the correct thing to do.",
